<title type="html"><![CDATA[Biography of Shaykh Dr. Alee Naasir al-Faqeehee]]></title>

<content type="html" xml:base="https://forum.salafiri.com/viewtopic.php?t=645&amp;p=688#p688"><![CDATA[
Full Name: <strong><span style="color: #0000FF">Ali ibn Muhammad ibn Nasir al-Faqeehi</span></strong><br /><br />He attended the Islamic University of Madeenah in 1381H and at that time <a href="http://salafitalk.net/st/viewmessages.cfm?Forum=11&amp;Topic=7068&amp;sortby=desc" class="postlink">Sheikh Abdul Azeez ibn Baaz</a> rahimahullaah was heading the university.<br /><br />Sheikh al-Faqihi has a doctorate in ‘Aqeedah and is currently Director of Scientific Affairs at <a href="http://qurancomplex.com/default.asp?l=eng" class="postlink">King Fahd Complex for Printing the Quran</a> and the Deputy Editor of the Journal of Qur’anic Research and Studies Magazine. The Shaykh is also a Professor at Islamic University of Madeenah and aTeacher in Prophet’s Masjid, Madeenah Al-Munawwara.<br /><br /><strong><span style="color: #0000FF">Some of his Teachers:</span></strong><br /><br /><em>    Haafidh al-Hakami<br />    Shaykh Ibn Baaz<br />    Shaykh Muhammad Khaleel Harraas<br />    Shaykh Muhammad Amaan al-Jaamee<br />    Shaykh Ahmed an-Najmee<br />    Shaykh Abdul Muhsin al-Abbaad</em><br /><br /><strong><span style="color: #0000FF">Some of his Students:</span></strong><br /><br />    Shaykh Falaah Ismaeel<br />    Shaykh Abdur Razzaq ibn Abdul Muhsin al-Abbaad<br />    Shaykh Abdullah al-Bukhari<br /><br /><strong><span style="color: #0000FF">Scholar’s Praise for him:</span></strong><br /><br />    On the website of Imaam Ibn Baz rahimahullah a list of the Shaykh’s prominent Students with their brief introductions is given. In that list the name of Shaykh Ali al-Faqeehee is also mentioned.<br />    Shaykh Salih as-Suhaymee has mentioned him among a list of Ulema’ here<br />    Shaykh Ubayd al-Jaabiree has mentioned him among a list of Ulema’ here<br />    Shaykh Muhammad bin Haadi has mentioned him among a list of Ulema’ here<br />    Shaykh Falaah Ismaeel also named Shaykh al-Faqihee as one of the Ulemah of Saudi Arabia here<br /><br /><strong><span style="color: #0000FF">Collection of his lectures and lessons:</span></strong><br /><br />Please click <a href="http://gate.gph.gov.sa/index.cfm?do=cms.scholarallsubjects&amp;schid=22359&amp;audiotype=lectures&amp;browseby=speaker" class="postlink">here</a>.<br /><br /><strong><span style="color: #0000FF">Books:</span></strong><br /><br />One of the books written by the Shaykh is entitled Al-Bida’ah. One of the books edited/verified by him is al-haydah [al-manaadharah al-kubra bayn ahl us-sunnah wal-firaq ad-daalah] by Imaam Abd ul-Azeez bin Yahya al-Makki al-Kinaani (d.264). The Shaykh has also checked the book The Book Of Forty Hadeeth Regarding The Madhhab Of The Salaf. In addition, the Shaykh has introduced the book Kun Salafian alal Jaadah (Be a Serious Salafi) that is written by Shaykh Abdus Salaam as-Suhaymee and is checked by Shaykh Saalih al-Fawzaan.<br /><br />Source: <!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="http://scholars-biographies.com/2013/09/18/biography-of-shaykh-dr-alee-naasir-al-faqeehee/">http://scholars-biographies.com/2013/09 ... -faqeehee/</a><!-- m --><p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="https://forum.salafiri.com/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=56">Shehzad Sattar</a> — Fri Nov 18, 2016 10:09 pm</p><hr />
]]></content>
